Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.39,0:00:48.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我畏惧在这一天的到来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.40,0:00:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秩序时代来临究竟谁能从中获得好处？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.61,0:01:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,君主将失去圣印魔法师将失去魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.62,0:01:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪纹使将失去邪纹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.54,0:01:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了这些人之外 普通人期盼着秩序时代来临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.25,0:01:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在极大混沌的时代  人类并肩作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.84,0:01:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对抗共同的敌人  混沌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.47,0:01:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  随着混沌日渐稀薄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.80,0:01:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类之间的斗争逐渐增加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.68,0:01:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得混沌彻底消失后会变成什么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.40,0:01:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使秩序时代来临想必还是会发生战争吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.40,0:01:37.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那是那个时代人类的选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.36,0:01:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸血鬼之王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.32,0:01:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之所以变成邪纹使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.66,0:01:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是为了在混沌的时代活下去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.79,0:01:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.62,0:01:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我打算今后也继续活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.88,0:01:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到永远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.84,0:01:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此  我必须击败你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.01,0:02:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此一来皇帝圣印就再也不会诞生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.23,0:02:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这活着是为了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.48,0:02:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是为活而活  跟死了有什么区别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.86,0:02:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我失去了邪纹  但心意不会变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.70,0:02:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要保护可爰的妹妹  拼上生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.83,0:02:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护生命而拼上生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.42,0:02:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这恐怕不行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.96,0:02:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不上不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.63,0:02:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是太无聊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.72,0:02:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.72,0:02:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈为保护我们死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.86,0:02:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼人愿意为了保护族人拼上性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.70,0:03:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为族  人报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.32,0:03:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.41,0:03:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊恩哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.50,0:03:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸血鬼之王？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.09,0:03:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是那家伙的本体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.55,0:03:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里的无非是分身之一罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.76,0:03:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真亏你能找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.72,0:03:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要杀了这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.56,0:03:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也会消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.06,0:03:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死心吧  吸血鬼之王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.16,0:03:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之所以能活下来  并非因为我是最强的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是因为我即使被杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.75,0:03:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要留下分身就能活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.88,0:04:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,—派胡言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.34,0:04:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要为母亲报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.78,0:04:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真愚蠢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.78,0:04:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.26,0:04:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.01,0:04:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.59,0:04:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.47,0:04:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你别碍事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.64,0:04:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡应该说过了  要拼上性命保护他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.69,0:04:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可不对我胃口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.20,0:05:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.62,0:05:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分身似乎会吸收接触到的人的生命力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.58,0:05:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请当心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢把大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.34,0:05:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可饶恕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.14,0:05:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然杀死本体也死不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.64,0:05:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把所有分身都消灭掉就得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.81,0:05:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定要灭了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.07,0:05:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸血鬼之王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.03,0:05:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,办得到吗  狼崽们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊恩露娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.59,0:06:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就只有你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.26,0:06:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你休想得逞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.52,0:06:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.25,0:06:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.23,0:07:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.11,0:07:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普莉希拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.88,0:07:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那光芒是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.80,0:07:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是圣杯的…普莉希拉的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.76,0:07:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样他就无法释放分身了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.97,0:07:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.31,0:07:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.39,0:07:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.65,0:07:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真招人恨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.82,0:07:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.53,0:07:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把你们的内藏全部吸收掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.46,0:08:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊恩哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.65,0:08:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸血鬼之王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.76,0:08:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.52,0:09:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  你怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.27,0:09:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊恩哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.56,0:09:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.19,0:09:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.53,0:09:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.53,0:09:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊恩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.67,0:09:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡大人  请当心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.75,0:09:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里还有分身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.17,0:09:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还留有一个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.63,0:09:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过邪纹快消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.97,0:09:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样就无法创造新分身了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.52,0:09:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾玛  露娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.02,0:09:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想怎么处置他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.27,0:09:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别...别杀我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.52,0:09:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想死我不想死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.07,0:09:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想死不想死不想死…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙好弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.82,0:10:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.20,0:10:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死妈妈和哥哥的不是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.83,0:10:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复仇已经成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.54,0:10:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.99,0:10:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了去埃兰姆吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.95,0:11:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是弗贝托斯吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.03,0:11:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.12,0:11:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想问你很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.12,0:11:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大圣堂惨剧的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.54,0:11:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟圣印教团及潘多拉的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.17,0:11:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我最想知道的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.13,0:11:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要阻止皇帝圣印诞生和混沌时代的终焉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.93,0:11:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想知道最终的答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.43,0:11:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就接触这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.26,0:11:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.77,0:11:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我想知道真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.81,0:11:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是必须知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.65,0:11:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我今后准备成就的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.44,0:11:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我陪您一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.78,0:12:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.61,0:12:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过  重要的是提欧大人的感受，
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.53,0:12:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.97,0:12:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.18,0:12:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是混沌仪内部吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.43,0:12:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被关起来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.35,0:12:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们并非实体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.15,0:12:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕只有意识进入了混沌仪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.98,0:12:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能让混沌的时代结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.57,0:12:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.78,0:12:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我名叫潘多拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.70,0:12:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潘多拉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.70,0:12:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能让混沌的时代结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为哪般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.35,0:13:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是传说中混沌爆发前繁盛过的史前文明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.14,0:13:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.90,0:13:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古代居然有这种文明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.86,0:13:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  传说曾经存在过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.69,0:13:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单看记录的话只能让人认为是凭空编造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混沌一旦消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.03,0:13:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能重现失传的技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.20,0:13:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在很久之后的未来  或许能找回这个文明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.71,0:13:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能让混沌的时代结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.17,0:13:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管拥有矛盾和问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.51,0:13:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这文明依然像一个生物一样不断成长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.01,0:13:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后终于获得了终极能量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.60,0:13:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们认为文明还会继续进步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.23,0:14:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这能量还提供给了兵器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.57,0:14:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好惨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.44,0:14:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文明越发达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.70,0:14:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许光明和暗影也越强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.16,0:14:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才说绝不能让混沌的时代结束吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.25,0:14:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了回避世界末日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.17,0:14:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们做出了一个决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.05,0:14:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即让混沌充满世界  破坏文明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.63,0:14:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.30,0:14:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混沌的时代一旦结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.30,0:14:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类早晚有一天还会得到终极能量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.48,0:14:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界便会消灭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.15,0:14:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能让混沌的时代结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.90,0:14:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这意味着终结的开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.11,0:14:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能让混沌的时代结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.53,0:14:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能让混沌的时代结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.00,0:15:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能让混沌的时代结束…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.43,0:15:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.55,0:15:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是史前文明的记录也是潘多拉这人的记忆吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.52,0:15:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时也是魔法师协会的理念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.77,0:15:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦混沌的时代结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.11,0:15:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史前文明的技术早晩会重现吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.82,0:15:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后创造出终极能量  被用在最终兵器上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.12,0:15:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混沌时代被带来的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.08,0:15:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及魔法师协会的理念  我已经理解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.42,0:15:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我的想法不会改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.80,0:15:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便在遥远的未来世界会毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.88,0:15:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不认为可以牺牲现在活着的人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.47,0:15:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及今后要出生的人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.68,0:15:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕这会成为终结的开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.27,0:16:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会选秩序的时代  而不是混沌的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.65,0:16:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白 我认为这样很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.82,0:16:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为提欧大人是为了解放饱受混沌之苦的人民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.49,0:16:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才成为君主的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.53,0:16:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.67,0:16:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝啊  这就是你的决定吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.38,0:16:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.43,0:16:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是终结的开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.71,0:17:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把瓦尔林德边境伯爵和哈鲁西亚公叫来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.42,0:17:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想发表皇帝即位宣言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.34,0:17:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  我向伟大的始祖君主莱恩和我的圣印发誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要登上王位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帝国的名字是莱恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.61,0:17:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这埃兰姆将定位帝都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.20,0:17:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是皇帝 也是人民的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.49,0:17:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的统治目标是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.70,0:17:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让所有入民安全地  公平地  幸福地生活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.21,0:17:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我在饱受混沌和暴政之苦的西斯迪纳时的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.21,0:17:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也许只是单纯的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.51,0:18:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  皇帝是秉承这一理念 朝这个目标前进的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.43,0:18:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将来若有违背这一理念的人当上了皇帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.85,0:18:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人民有摧翻他的权利 不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.98,0:18:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有义务推翻他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.15,0:18:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而人们也跟皇帝一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.95,0:18:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须遵守帝国的理念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.70,0:18:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以皇帝之名要求所有君主从属
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.42,0:18:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在所有圣印合为一体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.25,0:18:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的皇帝圣印诞生之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.38,0:18:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将宣告混沌时代结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.49,0:19:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至此  各位已结为夫妇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.91,0:19:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  请亲吻新娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.09,0:20:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此时此地  诞生了两对夫妇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.97,0:20:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝履行了约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.35,0:20:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将大圣堂的惨剧转变为了奇迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.31,0:20:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大陆已被统一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.19,0:20:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有圣印都到了皇帝手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.32,0:20:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 从此刻起 皇帝圣印宏伟纹章完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.40,0:21:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充斥着大陆的混沌就这样被净化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.86,0:21:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界获得了暂时的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.95,0:21:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,始祖皇帝将皇位让给第二代皇帝阿莱克希斯・德赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.12,0:21:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让其妃子马丽娜担任祭司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.87,0:21:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并将埃兰姆的统治交给了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.34,0:22:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退位的提欧•科尔内罗回故乡西斯迪纳当领主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.22,0:22:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让故乡幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.97,0:22:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他改变了世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.17,0:22:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直梦想看见这幅光景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.30,0:22:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.97,0:22:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人成功实现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.06,0:23:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡  我的魔女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.06,0:23:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是你的功劳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.69,0:23:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我这曾经的流浪君主施加了最美妙的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.04,0:23:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今往后  自然的时间会平静地流逝下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.04,0:23:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
